<title>USA: CDW Computer Q1 EPS $0.52 vs $0.26.</title>
<headline>CDW Computer Q1 EPS $0.52 vs $0.26.</headline>
<dateline>BUFFALO GROVE, Ill. 1997-04-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr			  $0.52		    $0.26</p>
<p> Net			 11,359		    5,534</p>
<p> Revs		     297,777		  206,705</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  21,682		   21,648</p>
<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: Quarters ended March 31</p>
<p>All numbers reflect the 3-for-2 stock split of July, 1996.</p>
<p>Net income reflects a $4 million non-recurring charge for the cost of exiting a company facility in 1996, and net income in 1996 and 1997 reflects adjustments to the executive incentive bonus pool.</p>
<p>Adjusted, earnings would have been $11.8 million or $0.55 a share, in 1997 Q1 and $7.5 million, $0.35 a share in 1996 Q1.</p>
<p>Full name of company is CDW Computer Centers inc</p>
